nion team|Oaks]], making his international debut at the [[2015 World Rugby Nations Cup]] in a match against the [[Namibia national rugby union team|Welwitschias]].<ref name= \"Romania Rugby Union debuts\">{{cite web | url=http://en.espn.co.uk/scrum/rugby/player/caps.html?team=12 | title= Romania Rugby Union debuts | date=15 April 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Career==\nBefore joining Timi\u0219oara Saracens, Randall Morrison played for [[Border Bulldogs]] and [[Golden Lions]].<ref>[http://www.sarugby.co.za/matchbreakdown.aspx?id=11019 MATCH BREAKDOWN - Eagles vs Border Bulldogs]</ref>\n\n==Honours==\n;[[Timi\u0219oara Saracens|Timi\u0219oara]]\n* [[SuperLiga (rugby)|SuperLiga]]: 2013, 2015\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commonscat}}\n*{{ESPNscrum|266973}}\n*{{Itsrugby profile|19212}}\n*{{Epcrugby profile|RM875837}}\n*{{SuperLiga profile|878}}\n* [http://rugby-timisoara.ro/jucator-rugby/ro/36/Randall-Anthony-MORRISON.html Randall Morrison] at [[Timi\u0219oara Saracens]] website\n\n{{Timi\u0219oara Saracens squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Morrison, Randall}}\n[[Category:1984 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from East London, Eastern Cape]]\n[[Category:Romanian rugby union players]]\n[[Category:Romania international rugby union players]]\n[[Category:Timi\u0219oara Saracens players]]\n[[Category:Border Bulldogs players]]\n[[Category:Golden Lions players]]\n[[Category:South African rugby union players]]\n[[Category:Rugby union flankers]]\n{{Romania-rugbyunion-bio-stub}}\n{{SouthAfrica-rugbyunion-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox rugby union biography\n| name = Randall Morrison\n| image = Randall Morrison 2018.jpg\n| image_size =\n| alt =\n| caption = Randall Morrison playing for Timi\u0219oara Saracens in 2018\n| fullname = Randall Anthony Morrison\n| nickname = \n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1984|02|12|df=yes}}\n| birth_place = [[East London, Eastern Cape|East London]], [[South Africa]]\n| death_date = \n| death_place = \n| height